sub_title: Plant Manager at Blackwood Engineering BELGIUM
summary:
Directing, managing and optimizing the overall operations of the plant. Working with the UK head office to set policies and make decisions guiding productivity, quality, and cost efficiency of plant operations.

Directs plant level support functions including engineering, materials, quality assurance, and human resources to ensure alignment with overall plant operations.
